dc_title_s: Phelps and Engisn's Travellers' Guide and Map of the United States
dc_description_s: 1 map : col. ; 40 x 93 cm.|Relief shown by hachures.|Engraved by: J. Wells, Brooklyn, L.I.|Map includes 15 very small insets with maps of vicinities of principal cities.|Includes diagrammatic views of principal rivers and mountains of the world.|Below map are scenes of events of American history, portraits of presidents and King Philip.|"Engraved on steel by J. Wells, Brooklyn, L. I."
